{"tid":2013840,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【深山仙人今日和你SING 做左示範，入黎學野！】","createTime":"2020-05-12T14:34:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-12T19:21:03.000Z","uid":176460,"like":88,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"29ac1382694a488b12981b2d088149725bad9c3a","tid":2013840,"uid":176460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T14:34:47.000Z","msg":"狗隊對付大仙都係用返同一招，提早兩粒鐘駐重兵守住唔俾你聚人<br />\n8:00 山友仙人一樣成功輕裝入場開波<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>仙人教你第一式：<span style=\"color: orange;\">因應場合選擇裝備</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個活動冇咩需要，現場又危險，咁咪輕裝上陣，俾佢SS都係搜空氣<br />\n<br />\n8:30 班狗第一次入商場，冇衝突，只有一兩個仙人走住黎屌<br />\n全數輕鬆退場，同時商鋪關既關，落閘既落閘<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">仙人教你第二式：<span style=\"color: orange;\">目標完成理撚得你</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n目標一：聚人延續抗爭氣氛，歌又唱完口號又叫埋，完成<br />\n目標二：攬炒商場冇生意做，完成<br />\n活動目標已經達成，唔需要同你糾纏，不戀戰不陣地，Be Water就係咁簡單<br />\n同埋記住，<strong>無論咩活動，都有一個超然既目標：最緊要人冇事</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n8:45 班狗撤退，9:15 山友仙人再聚再唱過歌<br />\n9:30 班狗再次入黎，指揮官周圍數人頭叫隻cam狗影低，準備捉限聚<br />\n<strong>最後一個都捉唔到</strong>，佢係四樓影上五樓搜證，到佢地上5樓準備做野果時已經冇哂人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>仙人教你第三式：<span style=\"color: orange;\">散聚有時咬我呀笨</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n散完再聚唔緊要，就算主要目標已經達成，只要聚完識得散，話事權就係我地到<br />\n<br />\n今日深山仙人們示範左俾你地睇<br />\n<strong>敵進我退，敵駐我擾，敵疲我打，敵退我追</strong><br />\n仙人寶刀未老，散水時機同速度依然值得學習<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能今日班狗真係放軟左手腳，但係無論如何，<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">做好自己先最緊要！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">學野啦！</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af9e23a21e72df1b114e9d0b53db76d9d25ebfd3","tid":2013840,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T14:36:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f24c93ca45af3d21906579db5f25cee0428e1cf","tid":2013840,"uid":25375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T14:39:19.000Z","msg":"好耐冇見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61ea3a020562dadb2668571bf177a9e132c03e8e","tid":2013840,"uid":108337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T14:44:28.000Z","msg":"全民空投 唯一出路<br />\n啲狗唔敢入邨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be98e9f94651f30a76f7166a3db3986494315c54","tid":2013840,"uid":60583,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T14:46:14.000Z","msg":"睇住立場live總結無人被綁架嗰下真係佩服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02df8e2b7c0eb9a8365e7e1850e68560e926964d","tid":2013840,"uid":89641,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T14:46:38.000Z","msg":"資深仙人哨表示今日行得好爽，有風有雨無咁焗，擔心慈中手足被打被拉，好開心你地夠醒目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e74a4a1a0fdf4f4aca4182dee234270cfad3ed9c","tid":2013840,"uid":44358,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T14:46:47.000Z","msg":"我最鍾意呢句<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">最緊要人冇事</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"7397d507d6c26940d00613e3c07f9fac027b2f6d","tid":2013840,"uid":89641,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"29ac1382694a488b12981b2d088149725bad9c3a","tid":2013840,"uid":176460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T14:34:47.000Z","msg":"狗隊對付大仙都係用返同一招，提早兩粒鐘駐重兵守住唔俾你聚人<br />\n8:00 山友仙人一樣成功輕裝入場開波<br />\n<span style=\"font