1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T14:50:12.000Z","msg":"要學既係個策略<br />\n策略好去邊個商場都一樣<br />\n大家都可以去返自己區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T15:04:17.000Z","msg":"你岩"},{"pid":"d0799d3c8dac864be3792cd5572fcb3621d725db","tid":2013840,"uid":222360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T15:05:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ff44c893cb9f6293d67cf5cd262fde88c4ed58e","tid":2013840,"uid":14494,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T15:16:43.000Z","msg":"諗起佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o2OT2O2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo2OT2O2.gif&h=a1551adf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3426cb765736f600d4ddae4b6a64a666004b5380","tid":2013840,"uid":229920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T15:17:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcf6f72580900c9c6af829750fe116e24501f69d","tid":2013840,"uid":1581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T15:18:53.000Z","msg":"小心有便衣狗就真"},{"pid":"3fa811e2fc49e8364793c4e878e75eb2a4627a38","tid":2013840,"uid":266672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T15:21:04.000Z","msg":"值得大家學習<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad1569bf56aa584f151e8f3e4f2b5fa14357d260","tid":2013840,"uid":1098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T15:24:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed36ba2cdf3ea125414886f9a7837306f60eb51d","tid":2013840,"uid":24367